  <brief_title>Study of Muscle Effects of BYM338 in Mechanically Ventilated Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Exploratory, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Study to Investigate the Effect of BYM338 on Muscle in Patients Requiring Prolonged Mechanical Ventilation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
